e </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">from the data </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">that there is a degree of consistency between the two and that for both Internet and particularly mobile, the incidence of </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">age </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">inappropriate content being seen is far lower than for the regulated TV market. </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Anecd</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">otally, from the hundreds of millions </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">of </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">contacts,</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">both in store and on help-lines, between customers and </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">the mobile operators’</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">across a very broad range of topics</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">, only a </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">small handful </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">are </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">rais</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">ed in a situation where a customer has </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">expressed concern about</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11